# Unreal Companion - {{project_name}}

This project uses **Unreal Companion** with the BMGD (Breakthrough Method for Game Development) methodology.

## Unreal Engine Integration

This project connects to Unreal Engine via MCP tools (87 tools available).

- Tools run through: AI → Python MCP Server (TCP:55557) → C++ Plugin → Unreal Editor
- Use `core_query` to search assets and actors
- Use `graph_batch` to add Blueprint logic
- Use `world_spawn_batch` to place actors
- Always use `/Game/` prefix for asset paths
- Vectors are arrays: `[x, y, z]` (Z-up, left-handed, cm/kg/degrees)

